
<div>
  <h1>Hi there, I'm DJ.</h1>
  <p>I'm a web developer looking for a company that is passionate about creative, self-motivated individuals that want to do great work while making the tech industry a more diverse, empathetic place.</p>
</div>

<div>
  <div style="vertical-align: top; display: inline-block; width: 48%;">

    <h2>Latest Posts</h2>

    <table>
      <% @posts.each do |post| %>

        <tr><td class="post-index-textbox">
          <figure class="tint" onclick="location.href =" + "#{post_path()}" ><%= link_to (image_tag("#{post.image}", width: "100%")), post %></figure></td>
        </tr>

        <tr><td class="post-index-textbox">
          <strong><%= link_to post.title, post %></strong> <span style="font-size: .75em; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"><%= post.created_at.to_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></span>
          <div style="font-size: .75em;"><%= post.dek %></div></td>
        </tr>

      <% end %>
    </table>
    <p>For more posts, please visit <%= link_to "the blog.", '/posts' %></p>
  </div>


  <div style="vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;  width: 48%;">

    <h2>Latest Projects</h2>

    <table>
      <% @projects.each do |project| %>


      <tr><td class="post-index-textbox"><figure class="tint" onclick="location.href =" + "#{project_path()}" ><%= link_to (image_tag("#{project.image}", width: "100%")), project %></figure></td></tr>

      <tr><td class="post-index-textbox">
        <strong><%= link_to project.name, project %></strong> <span style="font-size: .75em; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"><%= project.created_at.to_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></span>
        <div style="font-size: .75em;"><%= project.description %></div></td></tr>

      <% end %>
    </table>
    <p>To see all my projects, please visit <%= link_to "my portfolio.", '/projects' %></p>
  </div>
</div>

<div>
  <p>I am currently looking for full-time junior developer opportunities. If you are interested in bringing on a creative voice that cares deeply about improving tech and tech culture, <%= link_to "let's talk.", '/contact' %></p>
</div>
